    @Entity
public class CategorizedEvaluationDescriptor
extends EvaluationDescriptor<CategorizedEvaluationInstance>
    Define an evaluation as a categorisation. For instance : [ very bad ; bad ; acceptable ; good ; very good ], [true ; false], [off topic, irrelevant, relevant]
